ivardefs.name: period
ivardefs.desc: Time period when the contact point was/is in use.

ivardefs.name: rank
ivardefs.desc: Specifies a preferred order in which to use a set of contacts. Contacts are ranked with lower values coming before higher values.

ivardefs.name: system
ivardefs.desc: Telecommunications form for contact point - what communications system is required to make use of the contact.

ivardefs.name: use
ivardefs.desc: Identifies the purpose for the contact point.

ivardefs.name: value
ivardefs.desc: The actual contact point details, in a form that is meaningful to the designated communication system (i.e. phone number or email address).
